The player wakes up on the shores of the island. On the shores and nearby are strategically placed items to introduce the player to the different actions and mechanics of the game such as harvesting materials, crafting tools, hunting for food, consuming food, crafting shelter etc. This is done to give the player an immersive tutorial to help familiarize with the basic actions needed to progress in the game. The player may interact with various plants, animals, structures and other objects. Interaction between player and the environment is crucial for progression and ultimately escaping the island. 
